Run code file 1,3,4 to generate a graphml file
Use Gephi to import graphml file and process it to better visual the connection graph.

Overview tab:
Ranking -> Nodes -> Size -> weight -> Min:15, Max:30, Spline:3 -> Run 
Layout -> Fruchterman Reingold -> Run 
Layout -> Noverlap -> Run
Statistics -> Modularity -> Run
Partition -> Nodes -> Refresh -> Modularity Class -> Apply 
Font size: 10pt
Node size: Show node labels
Layout -> Label Adjust -> Run
Preview tab:
Nodes -> Border Color: #A0A0A0
Node Labels -> Show Labels: True, Font: 4pt
Edges -> Opacity: 40.0
Refresh; Export
